Annamalai\n&nbsp;University in India about \"Stress&nbsp;\nand&nbsp; Emotional&nbsp; Intelligence:&nbsp;\nA Study &nbsp;among&nbsp; Software&nbsp; Professionals&nbsp;\nin Chennai \".</li><li>“Emotional intelligence and leadership” by Suciu Sorin and\nVasile Gherhes form Polytechnic University of Timisoara]</li><li>Singing for Themselves By ALAN S. HOROWITZ SEPTEMBER</li><li>Who-was-more-important-Wozniak-or-Jobs,2018.[Online]. Available https://www.quora.com/Who-was-more-important-Wozniak-or-Jobs,\n[Accessed: 16- Nov- 2018].</li><li>McClelland, D. C. (1999), cf.\n&lt;https://www.talentsmart.com/media/ uploads/pdfs/ The_Business_\nCase_For_EQ.pdf&gt;.</li><li>16personalities,2018.[Online].Available\n&nbsp;https://www.16personalities.com/, [Accessed:\n16- Nov- 2018].</li><li>Scrum,2018.[Online].Available\n&nbsp;https://www.scrumguides.org/docs/scrumguide/v1/scrum-guide-us.pdf\n,[Accessed: 16- Nov- 2018].</li><li>Williams, Laurie (February 19–20, 2001). Ramsey, Dawn; Bourque,\nPierre; Dupuis, Robert, eds. <em>Integrating pair programming into a software\ndevelopment process</em>. 14th Conference on Software Engineering Education and\nTraining. Charlotte. pp. 27–36.</li><li>Salovey, Peter; Mayer, John; Caruso, David (2004),\n\"Emotional Intelligence: Theory, Findings, and Implications\", <em>Psychological\nInquiry</em>, pp. 197–215</li><li>Goleman, D. (1998). Working with emotional intelligence. New\nYork: Bantam Books</li><li>Petrides, K.V.; Pita, R.; Kokkinaki, F. (2007). \"The\nlocation of trait emotional intelligence in personality factor space\". <em>British\nJournal of Psychology</em>. <strong>98</strong> (2): 273–289.</li><li>Mayer, J.D.; Salovey, P.; Caruso, D.R.; Sitarenios, G. (2003).\n\"Measuring emotional intelligence with the MSCEIT V2.0\". <em>Emotion</em>.\n<strong>3</strong> (1): 97–105.</li><li>Mayer, John D (2008). \"Human Abilities: Emotional\nIntelligence\". <em>Annual Review of Psychology</em>. <strong>59</strong>: 507–536. </li><li>Petrides, K.V.; Furnham, A. (2003). \"Trait emotional\nintelligence: behavioral validation in two studies of emotion recognition and\nreactivity to mood induction\". <em>European Journal of Personality</em>. <strong>17</strong>:\n39–75</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><br>\n</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Use Emotional Intelligence Indicators With Team Formation -Research Paper', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'use-emotional-intelligence-indicators-with-team-formation-research-paper', '', '', '2019-06-14 19:08:39', '2019-06-14 18:08:39', '', 0, 'https://enghamzasalem.com/blog/?p=9', 0, 'post', '', 0);
