(13, 1, '2019-06-14 18:38:22', '2019-06-14 17:38:22', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Polymer 3 starter kit with login using Node JS — Part1</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Install the&nbsp;starter</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>· Open command line for example in in windows write CMD on Search Windows.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*X3NFAVVo4rpsZuMzxhg34A.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>· To create empty folder for the project write this Command</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>mkdir polymerMultiPage</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*7WmirLlbrQjcj-AssnKJQw.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Press enter and write:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>cd polymerMultiPage</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now you are inside the folder,to create your Polymer project using Git just write this command:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Git clone <a href=\"https://github.com/Polymer/polymer-starter-kit.git\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Polymer/polymer-starter-kit.git</a></p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To enter the folder &gt;&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Cd polymer-starter-kit</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now we will install the depndancy&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>npm install</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>launch the server and open the application:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>polymer serve</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>open <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8081\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://127.0.0.1:8081</a> or <a href=\"http://localhost:8081\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">http://localhost:8081</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>If you don’t have Git on your PC or you face any problem in permission just downalod form </em><a href=\"https://github.com/Polymer/polymer-starter-kit\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><em>https://github.com/Polymer/polymer-starter-kit</em></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>And copy past your folder to have this</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>c:/users/[Yourusername]/polymerMultiPage/polymer-starter-kit</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>you must see this&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*xENDAHYFLf0rNzRS6-2nZQ.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You have to see these files in the project&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*iY-tcNJBMaxUbv6fZwqmeg.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Inside src Folder you will find:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*ITlEFZlFD81p8eMRs18qMA.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>You can use Notepad++ or VS-code; in this tutorial I will use Notepad++ to make 